        <svcsubproc>
            <title>Horn(s)</title>
            <para>The single electric horn or optional dual electric horns, located at the base of the engine cowl,
                provide a means for the driver to signal a warning.
            </para>
        </svcsubproc>
        <svcsubproc>
            <title>Turn Signal Switch</title>
            <para>Turn signals provide a driver with the means to signal oncoming traffic or following vehicles of
                intended turns or lane changes.
            </para>
        </svcsubproc>
    </svcproc>
